psalm.text:
[[Ps 9,2]]I will give thanks to you, LORD, with all my heart; 
I will declare all your wondrous deeds.
[[Ps 9,3]]I will delight and exult in your name; 
I will sing hymns to your name, Most High.

[[Ps 9,4]]For my enemies turn back; 
they stumble and perish before you.
[[Ps 9,6]]You rebuked the nations and destroyed the wicked;
their name you blotted out forever and ever.

[[Ps 9,16b]]The nations are sunk in the pit they have made;
in the snare they set, their foot is caught.
[[Ps 9,19]]The needy will never be forgotten, 
nor will the hope of the afflicted ever fade.
